{
  "chapter": "099",
  "title": "刘敬叔孙通列传",
  "translations": {
    "1": {
      "title": "娄敬求见高帝",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">刘敬</span>，是<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>人。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">五年</span>，他戍守<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">陇西</span>，路过<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">洛阳</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高帝</span>正在那里。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">娄敬</span>卸下挽车的横木，穿着他的<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">羊裘</span>，求见<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>人<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">虞将军</span>说：\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>希望求见皇上陈述有利于国家之事。\" <span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">虞将军</span>想给他换上漂亮的<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">衣</span>服，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">娄敬</span>说：\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>若穿<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">帛</span>，就穿<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">帛</span>去见；若穿<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">褐</span>，就穿<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">褐</span>去见：始终不敢换<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">衣</span>。\" 于是<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">虞将军</span>入内禀告皇上。皇上召他入见，赐给他<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">食物</span>。"
    },
    "2": {
      "title": "劝都关中",
      "text": "随后询问<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">娄敬</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">娄敬</span>劝说道：\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">陛下</span>建都<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">洛阳</span>，莫非想与<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">周</span>王室比兴隆吗？\" 皇上说：\"是的。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">娄敬</span>说：\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">陛下</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">取得</span><span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>的方式与<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">周</span>王室不同。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">周</span>的先祖从<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">后稷</span>开始，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">尧</span>封他于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">邰</span>，积德累善十余代。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公刘</span>为避<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">桀</span>迁居<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">豳</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">太王</span>因<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">狄</span>人<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">侵伐</span>，离开<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">豳</span>，拄着<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">马箠</span>迁居<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">岐</span>，国人争相追随。等<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">文王</span>担任<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：姬昌\">西伯（姬昌）</span>，裁断<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">虞</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">芮</span>的诉讼，开始受命，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吕望</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">伯夷</span>从海滨前来归附。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">武王</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">讨伐</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">纣</span>，不约而在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">孟津</span>之上会合<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">八百</span>诸侯，都说<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">纣</span>可讨伐，于是灭了<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">殷</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">成王</span>即位，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">周公</span>等人辅佐他，就营建<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">成周</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">洛邑</span>，作为<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>之中心，四方<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span><span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">纳贡</span>来朝，道路里程均等，有德的就容易称王，无德的就容易灭亡。凡是居此地的，都要求<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">周</span>人务以德致人，不要依靠险阻，让后世骄奢而虐待<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">民</span>。到<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">周</span>盛世时，<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>和洽，<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">四夷</span>闻风来朝，仰慕德义怀念恩德，依附而共同侍奉<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>，不屯一卒，不<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">战</span>一<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>，<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">八夷</span>大国之<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">民</span>无不<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">宾服</span>，献上贡职。到<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">周</span>衰落时，分为东西两半，<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>不来朝见，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">周</span>也不能控制。并非它的德薄，而是形势弱了。如今<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">陛下</span>起于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">丰</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">沛</span>，聚集士卒<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">三千人</span>，便径直前行，席卷<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">蜀</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>，平定<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">三秦</span>，与<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项羽</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">战</span>于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">荥阳</span>，争<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">成皋</span>之口，大<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">战</span>七十次，小<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">战</span>四十次，使<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">民</span>肝脑涂地，父子的尸骨暴露荒野，不可胜数，哭泣之声未停，受伤的人未起，而想与<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">成</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">康</span>之世比隆盛，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>私下认为不可相比。况且<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>地山河环抱，四面关塞险固，一旦有急事，百万之众可立即调集。借助<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>故地的资源，这是极肥沃的土地，所谓天府之国。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">陛下</span>入关建都，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">山东</span>虽有乱，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>的旧地可保全。与人搏斗，不掐住他的喉咙，按住他的背部，不能全胜。如今<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">陛下</span>入关建都，据<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>故地，这正是掐<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>的喉咙按住它的背啊。\""
    },
    "3": {
      "title": "高帝从留侯议都关中",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高帝</span>询问<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">群臣</span>，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">群臣</span>都是<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">山东</span>人，争先说<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">周</span>朝称王数百年，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">二世</span>就灭亡了，不如建都<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">周</span>地。皇上犹豫不决。等<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">留侯</span>明确指出入关便利时，当日<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">车驾</span>西行建都<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">关中</span>。"
    },
    "4": {
      "title": "赐娄敬为刘氏",
      "text": "于是皇上说：\"本来主张建都<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>地的是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">娄敬</span>，'娄'就是'刘'啊。\" 赐姓<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">刘氏</span>，<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">任命</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">郎中</span>，号为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">奉春君</span>。"
    },
    "5": {
      "title": "谏阻击匈奴",
      "text": "<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">七年</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>王<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩王信\">信（韩王信）</span>反叛，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高帝</span>亲往<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻击</span>。至<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">晋阳</span>，听说<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩王信\">信（韩王信）</span>与<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">匈奴</span>欲共同<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻击</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>，皇上大怒，派人出使<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">匈奴</span>。<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">匈奴</span>把壮<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>肥<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">牛</span><span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">马</span>都隐藏起来，只见到老弱及瘦畜。使者接连十批回来，都说<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">匈奴</span>可攻击。皇上又派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">刘敬</span>再去出使<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">匈奴</span>，回报说：\"两国相攻，此时应当夸耀所长。如今<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>去，只见瘦弱老残，这必是要示弱，埋伏奇兵以争胜利。我愚见认为<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">匈奴</span>不可<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻击</span>。\" 这时<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>兵已越过<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">句注</span>，<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">二十馀万</span>大军已经出发。皇上大怒，骂<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">刘敬</span>说：\"<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>地俘虏！凭口舌得官，今又妄言阻挠我军。\" 将<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">敬</span>戴上刑具囚在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">广武</span>。于是继续前进，至<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">平城</span>，<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">匈奴</span>果然出奇兵<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">围</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高帝</span>于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">白登</span>，<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">七日（时长）</span>后才得以解围。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高帝</span>至<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">广武</span>，<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">赦免</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">敬</span>，说：\"我没听您的话，以致被困<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">平城</span>。我已把先前说可<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击</span>的十批使者都<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">斩</span>了。\" 于是<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">封</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">敬</span>食邑<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">二千户</span>，任为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">关内侯</span>，号为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">建信侯</span>。"
    },
    "6": {
      "title": "建议和亲",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高帝</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">罢兵</span>从<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">平城</span>归来，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>王<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：韩王信\">信（韩王信）</span>逃入胡地。当时，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">冒顿</span>为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">单于</span>，兵力强盛，控弦三十万，屡屡侵扰<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">北边</span>。皇上为此忧虑，问<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">刘敬</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">刘敬</span>说：\"<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>初定，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>卒疲于兵戈，不可以用武力征服。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">冒顿</span>弑父自立，将群母当作妻妾，靠武力立威，不可以用<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">仁义</span>来说服。唯一可行的是使其子孙长远作<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>子的办法罢了，只恐怕<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">陛下</span>做不到。\" 皇上说：\"如果真的可行，何为做不到！请问怎么办？\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">刘敬</span>回答说：\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">陛下</span>如果真能把嫡生的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">长公主</span>嫁给他，厚赠陪嫁，他知道<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>的嫡女并且陪送丰厚，<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">蛮夷</span>必然仰慕她为<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">阏氏</span>，生子必为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>，继任<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">单于</span>。为什么？因为他贪图<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>的厚币。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">陛下</span>每年都把<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>富余而他们稀缺的东西多次送去问候，趁机派能言之<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>以<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">礼</span>节讽谕。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">冒顿</span>在，他自然是女婿；死后，外孙就是<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">单于</span>。哪里听过外孙敢与外祖父抗<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">礼</span>的呢？可以不战而使<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">匈奴</span>渐渐<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>服。如果<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">陛下</span>不能派<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">长公主</span>，而让<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">宗室</span>及后宫之女冒称<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">公主</span>，他们也会知道，不肯尊贵亲近，没有益处。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高帝</span>说：\"好。\" 想派<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">长公主</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吕后</span>日夜哭泣，说：\"我只有<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>和一个女儿，为什么要抛弃她给<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">匈奴</span>！\" 皇上最终不能派出<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">长公主</span>，而取平民女子冒名<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">长公主</span>，嫁给<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">单于</span>。派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">刘敬</span>去缔结<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">和亲</span>之约。"
    },
    "7": {
      "title": "徙豪杰实关中",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">刘敬</span>从<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">匈奴</span>归来，于是说：\"<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">匈奴</span>在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">河</span>南<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">白羊</span>、<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">楼烦</span>王，距<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">长安</span>近的不过<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">七百里</span>，轻骑一天一夜就能抵达<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>中。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>中刚经战乱，人口少，土地肥沃，可以增加人口。诸侯当初起兵时，若非<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>地诸<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">田</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>地<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">昭</span>、<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">屈</span>、<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">景</span>就兴不起来。如今<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">陛下</span>虽建都<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">关中</span>，实际上人口少。北近胡寇，东有<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">六国</span>的<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">旧族</span>，势力强，一旦有变，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">陛下</span>也不能高枕而卧。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>希望<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">陛下</span>迁徙<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">齐</span>地诸<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">田</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>地<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">昭</span>、<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">屈</span>、<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">景</span>，以及<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">燕</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>的后裔，连同<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">豪桀</span><span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">名家</span>迁到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">关中</span>。平时可以防备胡寇；诸侯有变，也足以率领东<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">讨伐</span>。这是<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">彊本弱末</span>之术。\" 皇上说：\"好。\" 于是派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">刘敬</span>迁徙所言之人到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">关中</span>，共<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">十馀万口</span>。"
    },
    "8": {
      "title": "叔孙通秦时事",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">叔孙通</span>，是<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">薛</span>人。 <span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>时因<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">文学</span>被征召，任<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">待诏</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">博士</span>。 数年后，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">陈胜</span>起于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">山东</span>，使者把消息报告朝廷，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">二世</span>召见<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">博士</span>众儒生问：\"<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>戍卒<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">蕲</span>入<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">陈</span>，对诸位来说怎么看？\" <span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">博士</span>诸生<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">三十馀人</span>上前说：\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">人臣</span>不得聚众兴兵，聚众即是反叛，罪当死不可<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">赦</span>。希望<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">陛下</span>急速发兵攻击。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">二世</span>怒，面色大变。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">叔孙通</span>上前说：\"诸生说的都不对。如今<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>合为一家，已毁郡县城防，销毁兵器，向<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>表明不再用兵。况且明主在上，<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">法令</span>齐备于下，人人奉职，四方聚集，怎敢有反叛者！这不过是群盗鼠窃<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">狗</span>盗罢了，何足挂齿。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">郡守</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">尉</span>如今捕办就是了，何足忧虑。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">二世</span>高兴地说：\"好。\" 问遍诸生，有的说是反叛，有的说是盗贼。 于是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">二世</span>令<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">御史</span>查办诸说反叛者，认为不合时宜。 那些说盗贼的都免问。 于是赐<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">叔孙通</span><span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">帛</span>二十匹，<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">衣</span>一<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">袭</span>，<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">任命</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">博士</span>。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">叔孙通</span>出宫后，回到住所，诸生说：\"先生怎么这么奉承？\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">通</span>说：\"诸位不知道啊，我差点逃不出<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">虎</span>口！\" 于是逃离，前往<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">薛</span>，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">薛</span>已经降<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>了。 等到<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项梁</span>到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">薛</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">叔孙通</span>跟从他。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项梁</span>战败于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">定陶</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">叔孙通</span>改随<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">怀王</span>。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">怀王</span>做<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">义帝</span>，被迁到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">长沙</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">叔孙通</span>留下侍奉<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">项王</span>。 <span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">二年</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">汉王</span>率五<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>入<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">彭城</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">叔孙通</span>降<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">汉王</span>。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">汉王</span>战败而西退，于是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">叔孙通</span>始终跟随<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>。"
    },
    "9": {
      "title": "叔孙通变服事汉王",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">叔孙通</span>穿<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">儒服</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">汉王</span>憎恶；他于是改换服装，穿短<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">衣</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>式样，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">汉王</span>高兴。"
    },
    "10": {
      "title": "叔孙通举荐壮士",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">叔孙通</span>投降<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>时，跟从他的儒生<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">弟子</span>有<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">百馀人</span>，但<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">通</span>无所推荐，专推荐从前的群盗<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">壮士</span>。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">弟子</span>都私下骂道：\"侍奉先生数年，有幸跟从投降<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>，如今不能推荐<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>等，专门举荐大恶棍，为什么？\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">叔孙通</span>听到后，对他们说：\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">汉王</span>正冒着<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">矢石</span>争夺<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>，诸生难道能打仗吗？所以先举荐能<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">斩</span>将拔旗的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>。诸生且等等我，我不会忘记。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">汉王</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">任命</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">叔孙通</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">博士</span>，号<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">稷嗣君</span>。"
    },
    "11": {
      "title": "制朝仪",
      "text": "<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">五年</span>，已经统一<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>共同尊<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">汉王</span>为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">皇帝</span>于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">定陶</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">叔孙通</span>承担典礼名号的制定。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高帝</span>全部革除<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>朝苛刻的礼仪<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">法</span>式，使其简易。 <span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">群臣</span>饮<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">酒</span>争功，有的醉后乱呼，拔<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">剑</span>击<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">柱</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高帝</span>为此担忧。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">叔孙通</span>知道皇上日益厌烦，劝说皇上：\" <span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">儒者</span>难于攻<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">取</span>，可以一起守成。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>希望征<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">鲁</span>地众儒生，与<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">弟子</span>共同制作<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">朝仪</span>。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高帝</span>说：\"该不会很难吧？\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">叔孙通</span>说：\"<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">五帝</span>有不同的<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">乐</span>，<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">三王</span>有不同的<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">礼</span>。<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">礼</span>是随时代人情而加以节文规定的。所以<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">夏</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">殷</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">周</span>的<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">礼</span>的因袭损益可以知道，是说不相重复。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>希望略采古<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">礼</span>与<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>仪杂糅制定。\" 皇上说：\"可试着做做，让它容易明白，衡量我能施行的来做。\""
    },
    "12": {
      "title": "鲁两生不行",
      "text": "于是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">叔孙通</span>派人征召<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">鲁</span>地众儒生<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">三十馀人</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">鲁</span>有两位儒生不肯前往，说：\"您所侍奉者将近十主，都靠面谀以得亲贵。如今<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>刚定，死者未葬，伤者未起，又想兴起<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">礼乐</span>。<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">礼乐</span>的兴起，必须积德百年之后才可。我们不忍做您所做的事。您所做的不合古法，我们不去。您走吧，不要玷污我们！\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">叔孙通</span>笑着说：\"你们真是鄙陋的儒生啊，不知时势变化。\""
    },
    "13": {
      "title": "绵蕞野外习礼",
      "text": "于是与所征召的<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">三十人</span>一起西行，加上皇上身边有学问者和他的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">弟子</span><span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">百馀人</span>，在野外立<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">绵蕞</span>习演。演习<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">月馀（时长）</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">叔孙通</span>说：\"皇上可试着观看。\" 皇上观看后，让他们行<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">礼</span>，说：\"我能做这些。\" 于是令<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">群臣</span>演习，定在<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">十月</span>举行。"
    },
    "14": {
      "title": "朝仪成行",
      "text": "<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">七年</span>，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">长乐宫</span>建成，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">群臣</span>都在<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">十月</span>朝贺。仪式：先在天明前，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">谒者</span>主持<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">礼</span>仪，依次引领入殿门，廷中陈列<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">车骑</span>步卒宿卫宫廷，布置兵器张设<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">旗帜</span>。传令\"快走\"。殿下<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">郎中</span>夹阶而立，阶上有<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">数百人</span>。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">功臣</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">列侯</span>诸<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">将军</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">军吏</span>依次陈列在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">西方</span>，向东；文官<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">丞相</span>以下陈列在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">东方</span>，向西。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">大行</span>设<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">九宾</span>，胪传唱。于是<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">皇帝</span>乘<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">辇</span>出房，百官执持职事传呼警戒，引<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯王</span>以下至<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">六百石</span>的官吏依次奉贺。自<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯王</span>以下无不震惊恭敬。待<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">礼</span>完毕，又置<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">法酒</span>。侍坐殿上者都俯首，按尊卑次序起身上寿。<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">觞</span>酒九巡后，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">谒者</span>宣布\"罢<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">酒</span>\"。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">御史</span>执<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">法</span>举发不合仪者立刻带走。整个朝会置<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">酒</span>中，没人敢喧哗失<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">礼</span>。于是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高帝</span>说：\"我到今天才知道做<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">皇帝</span>的尊贵啊。\" 于是<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">任命</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">叔孙通</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">太常</span>，赐<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">金</span><span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">五百斤</span>。"
    },
    "15": {
      "title": "封诸儒生",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">叔孙通</span>趁机进言：\"诸位<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">弟子</span>儒生跟随<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>很久了，与<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>共同制作礼仪，希望<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">陛下</span>委任他们官职。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高帝</span>全部任命他们为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">郎</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">叔孙通</span>出来后，把<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">五百斤金</span>都分给诸生。诸生于是都欣喜地说：\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">叔孙生</span>真是<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">圣人</span>啊，了解当世的紧要事务。\""
    },
    "16": {
      "title": "为太子太傅",
      "text": "<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">九年</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高帝</span>迁<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">叔孙通</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">太子太傅</span>。 <span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">十二年</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高祖</span>想以<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>王<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">如意</span>替换<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">叔孙通</span>谏皇上说：\"从前<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">晋献公</span>因<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">骊姬</span>的缘故废<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>，<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">立</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">奚齐</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">晋</span>国大乱数十年，被<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>取笑。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>因不早定<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">扶苏</span>，让<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">赵高</span>得以假诏<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">立</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">胡亥</span>，自取灭国绝祀，这是<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">陛下</span>亲眼所见。如今<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>仁孝，<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>都知道；<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吕后</span>与<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">陛下</span>艰难共食，怎能背弃她！<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">陛下</span>若一定要废嫡立少，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>愿先<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">伏诛</span>，以颈<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">血</span>污地。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高帝</span>说：\"您算了，我只是开玩笑罢了。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">叔孙通</span>说：\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>是<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>的根本，根本一动<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>震动，怎么能拿<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>开玩笑！\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高帝</span>说：\"我听您的。\" 等到皇上设<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">酒</span>宴，见到<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">留侯</span>招来的宾客跟从<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>入见，皇上于是再无换<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>之意。"
    },
    "17": {
      "title": "定宗庙仪法",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高帝</span>驾崩，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孝惠</span>即位，便对<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">叔孙生</span>说：\"先<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">帝</span>的园陵寝庙的礼仪，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">群臣</span>都不熟悉。\" 调任他为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">太常</span>，制定<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">宗庙仪法</span>。此外逐步制定<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>朝各种礼仪<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">法</span>规，都是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">叔孙生</span>任<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">太常</span>期间讨论撰写的。"
    },
    "18": {
      "title": "谏修原庙",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孝惠帝</span>要向东朝<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">长乐宫</span>，其间时常往返，多次清道扰民，于是造<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">複道</span>，正在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">武库</span>南动工。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">叔孙生</span>奏事，趁机请求片刻时间问：\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">陛下</span>为何修<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">複道</span>通往<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">高寝</span>，使<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">衣冠</span>每月出游<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">高庙</span>？<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">高庙</span>是<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">太祖</span>，怎能让后世子孙走在<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">宗庙</span>的路上之上呢？\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孝惠帝</span>大惧，说：\"赶紧毁掉它。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">叔孙生</span>说：\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">人主</span>不做错事。如今已经造了，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">百姓</span>都知道了，现在毁掉，就显示有错误。希望<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">陛下</span>在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">渭</span>北建<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">原庙</span>，每月让<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">衣冠</span>出游那里，增广<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">宗庙</span>，这是大孝的根本。\" 皇上于是下诏<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">有司</span>建立<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">原庙</span>。 <span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">原庙</span>兴建，是因为<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">複道</span>的缘故。"
    },
    "19": {
      "title": "春尝樱桃",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孝惠帝</span>曾春天出游离宫，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">叔孙生</span>说：\"古时有<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">春尝果</span>之礼，如今<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">樱桃</span>成熟，可供献，希望<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">陛下</span>出行时，顺便采取<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">樱桃</span>献给<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">宗庙</span>。\" 皇上答应了。各种<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">果</span>的献祭由此兴起。"
    },
    "20": {
      "title": "太史公曰",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">太史公</span>说：俗话说\"<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">千金</span>的<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">裘</span>，不是一只<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">狐</span>的腋皮所成；<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">台榭</span>的椽子，不是一<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">木</span>的枝条所成；<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">三代</span>之际，不是一<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>的智谋所成\"。确实如此！<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高祖</span>起自微末，平定四海，谋略用兵，可谓竭尽其能。然而<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">刘敬</span>卸下挽车之辐一番进言，便建立万世之安，智慧岂是一人所能独占！<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">叔孙通</span>通达世事审度时务，制定<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">礼</span>仪讲究进退，与时<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">变化</span>，终成<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>家儒宗。\"大直若诎，道固委蛇\"，大概说的就是这个吧？"
    },
    "21": {
      "title": "赞",
      "text": "大厦借众木支撑，<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">裘</span>衣非一只<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">狐</span>所成。 卸挽辂献进言，立<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">绵蕞</span>陈礼书。 <span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">皇帝</span>始显尊贵，<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">车驾</span>西建都于关中。 既安定<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>，又和亲<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">匈奴</span>。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：娄敬\">奉春（娄敬）</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">稷嗣</span>，其功勋可堪流传。"
    }
  }
